msContents.summary: 355 original letters from Apollonio Bassetti written from Florence and Pisa to Anton Francesco Montauti, special envoy from Tuscany to the imperial court in Vienna. The last letter in this volume written by Bassetti is dated 18 April 1699, just five days before his death on 23 April 1699. The second volume is an eighteenth-century manuscript copy of these 355 letters.
